pageProduct.name: Thompson's One-A-Day Ginkgo 6000mg 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's One-A-Day Ginkgo 6000 supports mental alertness, concentration and memory.

Thompson's One-A-Day Ginkgo supports mental alertness, concentration and memory and may help maintain healthy cognitive performance in healthy individuals. It may
also assist peripheral circulation and promote general wellbeing.

Size: 60caps

Oil-Free?: Yes

Alcohol Free?: Yes

KEY FEATURES

• May help maintain healthy cognitive performance in healthy individuals
• Supports mental alertness
• Vegetarian/Vegan friendly
• May assist peripheral circulation
• Vegetarian/Vegan friendly

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each capsule contains: Herbal extract equiv. to dry:
Ginkgo biloba (Ginkgo) leaf 6g (6000mg)
std. to contain Ginkgo Flavonglycosides 29.4mg

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
